short" UTC="true">20130205T19:00:00</Date><Author type="string" label="Author's Name" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">RecSports</Author><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Height=""><![CDATA[<p><img alt="Title" height="38" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Activities/Sports/Events/Online/Real%20Bowling%20Title.png" title="Around the World Title" width="429" /><img alt="World Bowling" height="134" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Activities/Sports/Events/Online/bowling_600x450.jpg" title="Around the World Bowling" width="197" /><img alt="BYUI BOWLING" height="134" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Activities/Sports/Recreational/Bowling/Bowling.JPG" title="BYUI BOWLING" width="103" /><img alt="Bowling" height="133" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Activities/Sports/Recreational/Bowling/Bowling%204.jpg" style="float: left;" title="Bowling" width="106" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;Around the World Bowling gives online BYU-Idaho students all across the globe the opportunity to get connected to campus through RecSports. By following these steps you can join a team and bowl whenever, wherever!</p>
<ul>
<li>You will need a <a href="https://www.facebook.com/" title="facebook">Facebook</a> account to participate.</li>
</ul>
<p>Here's how it works:<br /><br />1. Read the <a href="Documents/activities/rec sports/Bowling Rules(0).pdf" title="Online Bowling Rules" target="_blank">Online Bowling Rules</a></p>
<p>2. "Like" the BYU-Idaho RecSports Activities page on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/recsportsactivities?ref=ts&amp;fref=ts" title="BYUI Activities Page" target="_blank">Facebook</a>!</p>
<ul>
<li>We will create your team for you. If you have any teammate requests please send us a message to BYU-Idaho RecSports Activities via Facebook.</li>
</ul>
<p>2. "Join" the weekly <a href="https://www.facebook.com/recsportsactivities/events">Online Bowling Event</a><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/564083943609288/?context=create"> </a>on the Facebook page.</p>
<ul>
<li>An online bowling event will be added under the icon "Events" each week.</li>
</ul>
<p>3. Bowl before the deadline each week.</p>
<ul>
<li>Deadlines will be Saturday at 11:59 pm each week.</li>
</ul>
<p>4. Upload a picture of your scorecard to the <a href="https://www.facebook.com/recsportsactivities/events">Online Bowling Event</a> page on Facebook.</p>
<p>5. Comment on your photo to verify your score.</p>
<ul>
<li>You will compete against each other by first individually bowling in your community. Your score will&nbsp; contribute to your team's points, and at the end of the week we will announce the winner.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>There will be a season followed by a tournament to find the champion of online bowling. Championship t-shirts are on the line! &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p></p>
<p>Let's get it started!</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="Component" Component="x16295" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="News" label="News" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="NewsNavigationComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_ContentSnippet" Name="ContentSnippet" label="Content Snippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false" Component="" CompTypes="ContentSnippet"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="ContentSnippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false" CompTypes="ContentSnippet"/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x6784" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" CompTypes="SiteControl"/></NewsDetail>
